Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然大家都为保卫蓝色的地球而拚命着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟快过年了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(本集在96年12月31日播出)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就休假了…就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛，是总集篇啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"机动战舰"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍着痛苦所踢起的小石头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若反弹回来也会变成钻石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.30,0:00:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上到手的梦想不算是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.01,0:01:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是请坚信它一定会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢从不气馁的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.02,0:01:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有想哭的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会永远永远在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.82,0:01:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GET BURNINC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的方式骄傲地去面对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.82,0:01:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去热衷的日子是梦的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GET BURNINC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那碎片收集起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能看见以明天为目标的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TO BE...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOING YOUR DAY'S GROW UP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"激钢人3"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想呼唤着明日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂的呼唤LET'S GO PASSION
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天将和平用这只手取回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LET'S GO 激钢人-3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像"热血卡通"般去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的抚子是特别节目吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是像介绍篇一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事也进行到转泪点了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以需要一集用来整理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真清楚啊，纯平
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是因为制作公司面临除夕忙不过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去，丈真现实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.28,0:02:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"抚子放送"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3  2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"抚子的为什么"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快点集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是抚子的秘密时间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点集合…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天特别告诉你有关抚子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我来说明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2195年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球面临最大的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体疏散!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以本舰撞击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘的无人兵器军团攻击并占领火星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更攻下了月球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至逼近地球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球联合军也似乎毫无办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此这就轮到抚子出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NERGAL重工独自开发机动战舰抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形式NERGAL ND-001
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全长298M
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全高106.8M
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:04:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全幅148M，总重量37530磅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收容人员2l4名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配备四座核脉冲引擎两座相转移引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中枢电脑使用SVC2027思兼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本配备大概是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请先从位于十二层甲板最上方的舰桥看起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的指令都是从这儿发出的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，今天是假日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰桥的正下方就是虚拟实境室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来说明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个房间是为了要纾解乘员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长期处在宇宙空间的精神压力而设置的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能自动测量各自的脑波还有其他资料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行精神分析
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后创造出适合那个人的剧情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里设定明人是和我同一个社团的学长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:04:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放轻松放轻松…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么紧张的话没办法纾解压力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是为了学长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为也有想在日常生活中除去烦恼的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也有个冥想室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第四甲板有娱乐室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连2l96年型最新式桌球台也有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有，隔壁有利用雷射投影的展望台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的风景，气压，氧气浓度可以自由选择
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那下方的厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷梅今天也在发挥她的手艺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来，加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是年底或过年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说让客人满意也是做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们非得认真地加油不可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟这不是在做生意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我自认手艺不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是职业的，完全不能比
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球看似狭小，其实很广大的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每块土地都有那块土地的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是我在臭盖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店抚子食堂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有地球三百个地方的调味料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样，厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红茶叶也搜集了最上等的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能够再放点酒那就更好喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督，不可以唷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之要推荐料理的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是放了一堆章鱼热狗的火星井吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我个人比较喜欢鸡肉饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不谈那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们抚子最骄傲的人型机械人AESTIVALIS的机库
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排排站的AESTIVALIS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小AESTI真的事情就交．给．我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从陆战模组开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗 这个直拳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳跃力也出类拔萃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的空战模组
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还更厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子的事交给我凯大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄就是得像这样才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有，看看这架势
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何能在空中飞就已经帅呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田，你不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系，没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后必胜绝技是众所皆知的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯，超级钩拳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没这么沸腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外这AESTIVALIS还有隐藏的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CROSS CRASH!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样世界的和平就安全啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在搞什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重装模组的话我和明人一起坐过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种重量感真叫人受不了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C战模组全部配备了四架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要驾驶员是天河明人，昴凉子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野光，真木泉这四人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能吧，十架才打中三架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来蚱蜢君的力场好像被强化了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会进化的机器?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近身战是我的本行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，天河怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:08:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候来救我们的是最新型的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么，是什么，这个模组
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新型的啊，喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发动机也很小巧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连肌肤也滑溜溜地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就搞一辈子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个以飞行员身份加入的赤月流行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及爱莉娜．金城．王\N这两人，好像有什么隐情…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份，目的一切不明的无人兵器群
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类将这初次遭遇的异星文明称为木星蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用入射角就行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"激钢射击"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之至今的经历是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有办法对迅速进化的木星兵器施以重击吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡通真好啊，充满梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是写实的战斗场面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来会怎么样发展呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么了，阿卡拉王子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然无法征服地球吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我正在收集有关地球人文化的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以便拟定作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球人的资料，有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我静候佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料部份就差不多这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟2l4人同吃同住会有各式各样的事情发生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各式各样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长和天河明人君之间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:12:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常抱歉，真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么地方受伤了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来舰长跟天河君是青梅竹马的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾经在哪里见过面吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，见过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，你肚子痛吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打架了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了，走开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我教你一个提起精神的诀窍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼晴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，你突然做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 居然在我不清楚的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明平常忙起来时都是我代理百合香工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了，冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊…年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这两个看来真是很速配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了什么才来火星的?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人，对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救不了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从上了抚子之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还是你第一次对我这么温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜，要振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人，你可以…吻我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香，你在胡说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人，只要你吻我 我会再加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会比现在更稍微卖力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人喜欢我对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人有各种复杂的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢，琉璃琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:14:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当大人也有很多好事唷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，你戴兔子帽很适合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的真是的，有各式各样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有"好事"吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人的好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们烦死了，给我差不多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河天河天河
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:15:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,载满各种想法前进的机动战舰抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后又将去哪里呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人相恋的命运又会如何呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉，真希望我能跟阿卡拉大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，阿卡拉大人看起来好像对我没兴趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有搜集到关于地球人文化的情报了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这部叫"机动战舰抚子"的卡通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为是调查地球人用的最好的样本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡通是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是把故事用图来表现印地球人的娱乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼，虚构故事这些脱离现实的东西真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊，天河
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球人也有男人跟女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战斗中萌芽的淡淡的恋情真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么爱呀恋情的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做这种事就能够打赢吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下等的地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个是什么，米耶米耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据资料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是叫做次元歪曲防壁的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一种利用护罩进行的敌阵突破攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠反作用力突破敌阵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到可以在这种地方发现打败激钢人的秘策
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好，米耶米耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您的夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡拉大人专用机大阿卡拉SPECIAL待命出动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢人你等着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘的飞行物体正急速接近研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张开护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做也没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次元歪曲防壁!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地震吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑，丈，明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是机械怪兽的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们立刻出击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，激钢人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出来的话我要下杀手了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.06,0:18:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LET'S GEKIGER IN
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢光束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西对我没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.83,0:18:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢剑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电浆断
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种玩具般的东西破不了这次元歪曲防壁的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧，激钢人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸，这样下去会打输的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈，最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然才刚完成还未测试
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这地步只好一搏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑，丈，明，用激钢爆炎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢爆炎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我为了防范于未然秘密开发的激钢爆炎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果没有一气呵成激钢人会爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样的话也只能干了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢爆炎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个光芒是?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡拉大人 请快点逃 阿卡拉大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，地球人给我记着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好，各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 博士 你什么时候想出那种武器的?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这阵子在抚子里演的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 博士也在看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了，快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年夜面正等着你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面，也有年糕吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是明天才吃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"完"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗?这种结束方式?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是如此 下集也请继续收看…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的感动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:21:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有纯粹的情感沉睡其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要追寻梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容与泪水的数目就会渐渐增多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时想要更像自我地去感受风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不属于其他人的我自己的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要去发掘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我是御统百合香的配音员 桑岛法子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然低温每天持续着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观赏机动战舰抚子的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把冷风什么的用次元歪曲防壁吹散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.89,0:22:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着次回木星蜥蜴的真面目似乎终于明了了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么样的故事呢? 我现在就好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香还有出场吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，次回机动战舰抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"遥远星球来的男友"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么说定啰
